title: Star Wars: The Clone Wars
fullTitle: Star Wars: The Clone Wars (TV Series 2008–2020)

episodes.title: Holocron Heist
episodes.plot: Darth Sidious commissions a bounty hunter to break into the Jedi Temple Archives.

episodes.title: Cargo of Doom
episodes.plot: With Anakin and Ahsoka in pursuit, Cad Bane seeks the last piece to unlock the holocron he stole for Darth Sidious.

episodes.title: Children of the Force
episodes.plot: With the information from the stolen holocron, Darth Sidious orders Cad Bane to kidnap several Force-sensitive children for his scheme.

episodes.title: Senate Spy
episodes.plot: At the Jedi High Council's request, Padmé investigates a Separatist conspiracy in the Senate.

episodes.title: Landing at Point Rain
episodes.plot: Anakin, Ahsoka, Obi-Wan and Ki-Adi-Mundi lead a landing party to destroy a droid factory on Geonosis.

episodes.title: Weapons Factory
episodes.plot: Luminara and Anakin act as decoys to divert new enemy super-tanks, while Padawans Barriss Offee and Ahsoka attempt to destroy a Separatist droid factory.

episodes.title: Legacy of Terror
episodes.plot: Luminara Unduli disappears during a sandstorm while following Poggle the Lesser. When Anakin and Obi-Wan track her to an ancient temple, they are attacked by undead Geonosian warriors.

episodes.title: Brain Invaders
episodes.plot: Ahsoka, Barris and Tango Company board a supply ship to a station near Ord Cestus. But one of the troopers has been infected by a Geonosian brain worm and has taken along a nest full of worm eggs to submit the others.

episodes.title: Grievous Intrigue
episodes.plot: Master Eeth Koth has tracked down General Grievous, but is soon captured and tortured as an example to the Jedi. Obi-Wan, Anakin and Adi Gallia mount a rescue attempt, unaware that Grievous is expecting them to do just that.

episodes.title: The Deserter
episodes.plot: Obi-Wan and a detachment of the 501st track down General Grievous on Saleucami. When Captain Rex is injured he is taken to a farmhouse to recuperate, only to find the farmer has a familiar face.

episodes.title: Lightsaber Lost
episodes.plot: During a mission in the underworld of Coruscant, a pickpocket steals Ahsoka's lightsaber. Too ashamed to tell Anakin, she sets out to look for the thief alone, but gets help from Tera Sinube, an ancient Jedi Master.

episodes.title: The Mandalore Plot
episodes.plot: Firmly opposed to war, Duchess Satine of Mandalore heads the Council of Neutral Systems. Obi-Wan Kenobi investigates rumors of the resurgence of the so-called Death Watch on her planet.

episodes.title: Voyage of Temptation
episodes.plot: Obi-Wan and Anakin guard the Duchess Satine and members of The Council of Neutral Systems as they travel to Coruscant aboard the luxury vessel Coronet, but a traitor amongst them has smuggled aboard a spider-shaped assassin droid.

episodes.title: Duchess of Mandalore
episodes.plot: On Coruscant, word reaches Duchess Satine that Death Watch is mobilizing, sparking a preemptive Republic invasion. On the run from Republic authorities, Satine and Obi-Wan set off to discover the group's true motives.

episodes.title: Senate Murders
episodes.plot: Padmé is working to to introduce a bill to minimize military spending and halt the creation of clone troopers. But when one of her most trusted allies is poisoned, she and Bail Organa set out to expose the murderer.

episodes.title: Cat and Mouse
episodes.plot: Anakin is tasked to fly a prototypical cloaked ship to get supplies to Bail Organa on Christophsis, but can't resist an urge to attack a blockade headed by the infamous Admiral Trench.

episodes.title: Bounty Hunters
episodes.plot: Obi-Wan, Anakin and Ahsoka crash land on Felucia and reluctantly join four bounty hunters in defending a village from Hondo Ohnaka's pirate gang.

episodes.title: The Zillo Beast
episodes.plot: When the Republic detonates a powerful electro-proton bomb to settle the battle of Malastare, it accidentally wakens an ancient and thought to be extinct Zillo Beast.

episodes.title: The Zillo Beast Strikes Back
episodes.plot: The Zillo Beast has been captured and is brought to Coruscant for testing. Chancellor Palpatine wants to learn the secrets of its invulnerability but only manages to make the beast angry enough to escape.

episodes.title: Death Trap
episodes.plot: Determined to have his revenge on Mace Windu, Boba Fett infiltrates Jedi cruiser Endurance as part of a group of young clone cadets.

episodes.title: R2 Come Home
episodes.plot: When Anakin and Mace try to rescue Admiral Kilian from his crashed cruiser, they walk into a trap set by Boba Fett and his bounty hunter associates. Then it is up to R2-D2 to try and get a message out.

episodes.title: Lethal Trackdown
episodes.plot: Boba Fett and Aurra Sing are using hostages to force Mace Windu to face them. With Mace and Anakin still recovering, Plo Koon and Ahsoka Tano track down the bounty hunters.
